eaching-al-taleem"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1mC","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":43635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/05\/islam-light-unto-the-nations\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Fiqh: Understanding Islam a light unto the nations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhomever Allah intends goodness for, He grants him understanding of the religion.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2645 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi Imam al-Ajurri commented, \u201cThus, when Allah Almighty intended goodness for them, He granted them\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35273,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/20\/arrogant-with-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: People will be arrogant with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas ibn \u2018Abdul Muttalib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe religion will be victorious until you pass beyond the seas and fight upon the seas in the way of Allah, then after you will come people who recite the Quran. They will say:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2991,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/22\/nations-destroyed-deen-extremism\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Religion: Nations destroyed by religious extremism","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cO people, beware of exaggeration in religion, for those who came before you were ruined by exaggeration in religion.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3029 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani Ahmad ibn Hanbal said, \"Do not exaggerate in anything, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39723,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/13\/deen-naseehah\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nasihah: Islam is goodwill to Allah and the people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said three times, \u201cThe religion is sincere goodwill.\u201d They said, \u201cTo whom?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo Allah, to His Book, to the leaders of the Muslims and their common people.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1926 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28831,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/tafsir-quran-ignorance\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tafsir: Warning not to interpret Quran without knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever speaks on the Quran without knowledge, let him take his seat in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2950 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31823,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ibn-abbas-quran-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":5246,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Whims: The Quran casts blame upon lowly desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty did not mention whims in any place in his book but that he cast blame on it.\u201d Source: Dhamm al-Hawa\u0301 1\/36 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0632\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u063